<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
      }
      .box1 {
        width: 100%;
        height: 200px;
        background-color: #8783f5;
      }
      .successContainer {
        width: 300px;
        height: 400px;
        background-color: white;
        z-index: 1;

        position: relative;
        top: -100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .dot-line {
        width: 80%;
        border-top: 1px dashed #8783f5;
        margin: 10px auto;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none; /* 리스트 스타일 제거 */
        padding: 0; /* 내부 여백 제거 */
      }
      ul li {
        text-align: justify; /* 양쪽 정렬 */
      }

      .success-icon {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
      }
      .success {
        display: block;
        margin: 20px auto;
        width: 300px;
        height: 40px;
        border: 1px solid #8783f5;
        background-color: #8783f5;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: white;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      /* 모바일 */
      @media screen and (max-width: 500px) {
        .success {
          width: 150px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }
      }

      /* 테블릿 */
      @media screen and (max-width: 800px) {
        .success {
          width: 200px;
          font-size: 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="box1"></div>

    <div class="successContainer">
      <img
        src="https://kdt8-cs.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8%ED%95%98%EC%B9%B4_icon/CheckCircleFill.svg"
        alt="완료"
        class="success-icon"
      />
      <h1 style="font-size: 24px">결제 성공</h1>
      <hr class="dot-line" />
      <p>결제가 성공적으로 완료되었습니다.</p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          주차장
          <div><%= result.shareparking.shareparkname %></div>
        </li>
        <li>
          결제금액
          <div><%= result.payamount %>원</div>
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <button class="success" onclick="home()">확인</button>
    </div>
    <script>
      function home() {
        location.href = "/";
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
